            <h2 class="text-primary font-monospace text-decoration-underline">NFC Security</h2>
            
            <p>After NFC data has been transferred in from the POS app onDeactivated() is called, in this function I reset the message data to an empty string. This stops attacks from scanning the POS a second time in an attempt to steal their receipt information.</p>

            <p>After NFC data is sent, the POS now goes to a new page which allows the POS to re-send the receipt data if there was a problem with the customers receiving the receipt information. Alternatively, the POS can finish the transaction and the app will return to the start page.</p>
        </div>

