            <p>Added a vendor page to the POS to allow a user to select which shop they are in, this is to allow for a wider range of receipts to demo the Pop application such as supermarket goods or high end laptops.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-5">
            <h2 class="text-primary font-monospace text-decoration-underline">Removing From SQLite</h2>

            <p>Had problems removing receipts from the local SQLite database on link of a receipt. Found that by deleting based on UUID was having no effect but by using a receipt ID value, the row was being dropped successfully. Instead of looking further into this, I was happy to stick with the variable change.</p>
        </div>

